{
  "page": "Beryl",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Beryl</b> is a mineral used for ornamentation. It can appear in various colors, such as green for <a href=\"/index.php/Emerald\" title=\"Emerald\">emeralds</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Beryl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Beryl&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a> gives <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> a thousand miniature <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> made of beryl, <a href=\"/index.php/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">jade</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Onyx\" title=\"Onyx\">onyx</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Tourmaline\" title=\"Tourmaline\">tourmaline</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Amber\" title=\"Amber\">amber</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Opal\" title=\"Opal\">opal</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Amethyst\" title=\"Amethyst\">amethyst</a>, with armor of <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h